# AI PDF Summarizer

AI PDF Summarizer is a Flask-based web application that uses Ollama and the Phi3 AI model to generate intelligent summaries from PDF documents. Users can upload PDFs, select summary size and language, and download the generated summary as a PDF file.

---

# Features

* Upload PDF documents
* AI-generated summaries
* Multiple summary sizes

  * Little
  * Medium
  * Full
* Multi-language support

  * English
  * Spanish
  * French
  * Arabic
* Download summary as PDF
* Modern responsive UI
* Local AI processing using Ollama

---

# Technologies Used

* Python
* Flask
* PyPDF2
* Ollama
* Phi3 AI Model
* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* ReportLab

---

# Installation

## 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/ai-pdf-summarizer.git
cd ai-pdf-summarizer
```

---

## 2. Install Required Packages

```bash
pip install flask PyPDF2 requests reportlab
```

---

## 3. Install Ollama

Download and install Ollama:

* Windows / Mac / Linux:
  https://ollama.com

---

## 4. Pull Phi3 Model

```bash
ollama pull phi3
```

---

## 5. Run Ollama

```bash
ollama run phi3
```

Keep Ollama running in the background.

---

## 6. Run Flask Application

```bash
python app.py
```

---

# Open in Browser

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5000
```

---

